OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780128433
OL,3,CKing's College Hospital opens outdoor
OL,4,Croof garden for critically ill patients
OL,6,FKing's College Hospital has become the
OL,7,Ffirst hospital in the UK to open an
OL,8,Foutdoor critical care garden on its
OL,9,Froof, allowing patients to experience
OL,10,Fbeing outdoors.
OL,12,FThe green space has been designed
OL,13,Fespecially to allow critically ill
OL,14,Fpatients to safely be in the open-air,
OL,15,Fwithout being disconnected from
OL,16,Fessential life-support systems.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
