OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780128433
OL,3,CKing's College Hospital opens outdoor
OL,4,Croof garden for critically ill patients
OL,6,FDr Tom Best, Clinical Director of the
OL,7,Fhospital's critical care unit, says
OL,8,Fthat many severely unwell patients
OL,9,Fspend "weeks or even months in
OL,10,Fcritical care", undergoing "intensive
OL,11,Fand often invasive treatment".
OL,13,FDuring that time, many experience
OL,14,F"hallucinations or delirium" inside
OL,15,Fthe hospital environment, which Dr
OL,16,FBest says "can be extremely
OL,17,Ffrightening and delay recovery".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
