PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780128433
OL,3,CKing's College Hospital opens outdoor
OL,4,Croof garden for critically ill patients
OL,6,F"Research shows that time spent in
OL,7,Fnature can reduce delirium, improve
OL,8,Frecovery outcomes, and lift the
OL,9,Fspirits of patients and their
OL,10,Ffamilies", he adds.
OL,12,F"It's important to treat the whole
OL,13,Fperson and this outdoor critical care
OL,14,Funit helps meet our goal of caring for
OL,15,Fthe mind as well as the body."
OL,17,FThe garden has partly funded by a #2
OL,18,Fmillion donation from King's College
OL,19,FHospital Charity, as well as by the
OL,20,Fhospital trust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
