OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780128433
OL,3,CKing's College Hospital opens outdoor
OL,4,Croof garden for critically ill patients
OL,6,FThe roof-top area is located on top of
OL,7,Fthe hospital's 60-bed critical care
OL,8,Funit and has space for up to six
OL,9,Fpatient beds.
OL,11,FBeds can be pulled up next to
OL,12,Fspecially designed weatherproof
OL,13,Fmedical cabinets housing power, data
OL,14,Fand medical gas supplies.
OL,16,FThe garden will also allow research to
OL,17,Fbe conducted into how exposure to
OL,18,Fsunlight, fresh air and greenery
OL,19,Flowers blood pressure, reduces stress
OL,20,Fand improves patient wellbeing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
